parameters: フィルター識別名 = oldfilm

『Mama』: You seem to be in a good mood today. Vita is also
doing well... How are you feeling?

'Mama': Oh my, 'Are you in a good mood?' Hehe... If you have
such a lovely expression, I can't help but smile too.

'Mama': When you grow a little more... let's move to the
bigger one over here. It's getting a bit cramped there,
isn't it?

'Mama': What's wrong...? Are you worried? Don't worry,
there's nothing to be concerned about. Besides, I can
provide a better environment over here...

'Mama': Oh... you're such a scaredy-cat... But don't worry,
because 'Mama' is here with you, let's do our best, okay?

'Mama': That's right... Keep it up. Once you grow a little
more, you'll be able to go outside.

'Mama': The outside world can be scary and full of
uncertainties... But I believe that you can become 'happy'.
I believe that you can become a wonderful girl.

'Mama': Hehe... You have a surprised look on your face... It
was a little difficult, wasn't it? But someday, it will be
just as I said... I'm sure of it.

'Mama': Once you grow up and can go outside... I'm thinking
of giving you a 'name'.

'Mama': Oh... Are you curious? But I won't tell you just
yet. It's a 'celebration' for being able to come out from
here.

'Mama': Hehe... Are you getting sleepy? Shall we end today's
'chat' here for now?

Kind... warm... and very smart... 'Mama' taught me
everything.

Every time 'I' grew a little closer to becoming an adult...
'Mama' had a truly happy expression. Seeing that face...
made me happy too.

She said she would give me a 'name'. I wonder what kind of
'name' it will be... I'm curious. It would be nice if it's
cute... or maybe something elegant... That would be nice...

'Mama'... She said she couldn't have children of her own.
So, she said she created 'me'. She said she wanted to give
'me' love no matter what.

I'm sorry for involving you in my 'ego'. So, when you grow
up and can leave here... There's something I want to tell
you first.
Thank you... for giving birth to me.
フィルター識別名 = noize
